      "message": "Looking through SkVx.h, I don\u0027t see any reason for mad(a,b,c) to exist instead of just writing out a*b+c.  Why don\u0027t we warm up with a CL to remove mad() entirely?\n\nIf we can\u0027t remove this for some reason, just return f*m+a?",
