        "id": 11929
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-30T20:48:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Okay, I will take note to create a CL to remove mad(a,b,c) from SkVx.h and any of its uses in Skia code. \n\nFor this CL, I switched to using \n  return f*m+a;\n\nand tested that it does indeed work.",
      "parentUuid": "3a8f7e0b_8f63c6f3",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 636,
